QuestData.Title: Mushan Mastery
QuestData.Description: Mushan! Would ya look at the size o' 'em. Old as the dirt they walk on probably. A fine trophy.$b$bIf you are lookin' to test your mettle as a big game hunter, start with them.
QuestData.CompletionText: They didn't send ya' runin' did they?
QuestData.RewardText: Well done $p.$b$bMy father travels across the sea to a new continent and all he can seem ta' want to hunt is old borin' wolves.$b$bMe, I like to hunt stuff with meat on its bones.
